text: Marek Baránek (born March 1, 1995) is a Czech professional ice hockey player. He is currently playing for HC Karlovy Vary of the Czech Extraliga. Baránek made his Czech Extraliga debut playing with HC Litvínov during the 2014–15 Czech Extraliga season. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:HC Litvínov players Category:HC Karlovy Vary players Category:Czech ice hockey defencemen Category:Sportspeople from Ústí nad Labem
